column.description:
Fully qualified name of the class which can be used to
					create a customized table model. It must be a child of {@link
					com.adventnet.client.components.table.web.CustomTableModelRenderer}

Fully Qualified name of the Class for row level
					transformations. It must be a child of {@link
					com.adventnet.client.components.table.web.RowTransformer}

table.description:
It has the information for constructing a criteria by
			logically binding the various conditions provided in {@link
			ACRELATIONALCRITERIA} using {@link #LOGICALREPRESENTATION}

column.description:
Data will be fetched for the parameter according to the
					given scope.
					if 'SCOPE' is 'STATIC' then 'VALUE' will be considered,
					if 'SCOPE' is 'STATE' then value will be fetched from state param,
					if 'SCOPE' is 'REQUEST' then value will be from request,
					if 'SCOPE' is 'DATAMODEL' then value will be fetched from tablemodel
					Default 'SCOPE' is 'STATIC'
